cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper discusses digital watermarking as a solution to protect intellectual property of neural network models from unauthorized redistribution or prediction services. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper focuses on deep learning models and their value as intellectual properties. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is another possible category as deep learning models are often used in computer vision tasks. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a potential category as watermarking is a common technique used in multimedia applications. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the vulnerability of neural network models to attacks and proposes a new watermarking method to improve their security.
